1.  **Dynamic Document Settings**: I updated `InvoiceTemplate.tsx` to fetch company details (Name, Address, Phone, PIN) from the system settings (via API and LocalStorage cache). This ensures that any changes made in the **Settings Manager** are immediately reflected in all generated documents (Receipts, Invoices, Waybills, Quotes) without code changes.
2.  **View Receipt Functionality**: I updated `SalesHistory.tsx` to make the "View Details" (Eye Icon) button functional. It now opens a modal displaying the receipt preview, allowing you to verify details before printing.

