To ensure compatibility with standard **80mm POS Thermal Printers**, I need to modify the `InvoiceTemplate`.

Currently, the system generates **A4 (210mm)** documents by default, which will look tiny and unreadable when shrunk down to a thermal printer receipt.

I will update **`components/admin/InvoiceTemplate.tsx`** to detect if the document type is `RECEIPT`. If it is, it will render a specific **80mm optimized layout** (narrow width, single column, high contrast, monospace font) instead of the A4 layout. All other types (Invoices, Quotes, Waybills) will remain A4.

